About Us

Health information without the clutter

pIRfusiX solutions is a health monitoring system that measures a patients blood oxygen levels. This data is then transmitted via cellular, satellite or wifi and visualized using our website. Our objective is to allow practitioners to prepare for oncoming patients from remote locations by providing realtime data and trend predictions regarding the patients condition.

Our Team

Jeffrey Roszell - Project Manager and Firmware Lead

Youssef Maksoud - Full Stack Developer

Randy Moore - Sensor hardware Lead

Khaled Elmalawany - Sensor, Firmware Developer

Ryan Ward - Gateway Lead
